{"by":"donatj","id":47764412,"parent":47762864,"text":"I can <i>almost</i> almost understand the logic behind not backing up OneDrive&#x2F;Dropbox. I think it&#x27;s bad logic but I can understand where it&#x27;s coming from.<p>Not backing up .git folders however is completely unacceptable.<p>I have hundreds of small projects where I use git track of history locally with no remote at all. The intention is never to push it <i>anywhere</i>. I don&#x27;t like to say these sorts of things, and I don&#x27;t say it lightly when I say someone should be fired over this decision.","time":1776167579,"type":"comment"}